{"tid":2305888,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"廣東話好好聽啊！- 高慧然","createTime":"2020-11-30T04:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T04:46:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3785adee361abeef367a0a8a5162fdd33274fb1","tid":2305888,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:37:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201130/YOEOE43O4FFQLF2GFEK5ZWG34U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201130%2FYOEOE43O4FFQLF2GFEK5ZWG34U%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=1ccaa60f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201130%2FYOEOE43O4FFQLF2GFEK5ZWG34U%2F&h=8db70b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201130/YOEOE43O4FFQLF2GFEK5ZWG34U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n廣東話好好聽啊！- 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jb21Ju4tSiMBz3VohOp4lOn7cwU=/828x577/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5YG75WSXHJEWZH7H4VJGBKAPEQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjb21Ju4tSiMBz3VohOp4lOn7cwU%3D%2F828x577%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5YG75WSXHJEWZH7H4VJGBKAPEQ.png&h=2b68ef06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nfb（@DrMcDowallACT）短片截圖<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭召開新一屆國會，議員宣誓時，竟傳出廣東話誓辭！原來，當地國會容許議員選擇兩種語言宣誓，今年10月當選的小型政黨ACT國會議員James Samuel McDowall分別使用英文及廣東話讀出他的誓辭。<br />\n<br />\nMcDowall在紐西蘭出生，是土生土長的白人。但是，這段廣東話誓辭卻讀得相當流利，除了一兩個字有少許走音，整體可用「標準」來形容。<br />\n<br />\n早在今年7月，McDowall就以ACT外交事務發言人身份發表聲明，支持紐西蘭政府因應《港區國安法》而暫停與香港的引渡協議。McDowall也曾提出紐西蘭政府應該參考英國的做法，為BNO持有人提供移居和延長簽證的措施。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。但是，當紐西蘭國會廳傳出廣東話宣誓，的確令香港人意外又感動。我忍不住輕嘆：廣東話好好聽啊！香港跟紐西蘭一樣，曾屬英聯邦國家/地區，英文及廣東話是香港人的法定語言。McDowall對香港人的支持，對廣東話這種語言的尊重，讓香港人銘感於心。<br />\n<br />\n極權統治下，一步一步消滅我們的語言、文字、文化是不難預見的。每一個香港人都肩負着重任，把我們的語言、文字、文化傳承下去。有一天，即使香港人像猶太人那樣散落世界各地，廣東話、廣東話俚語、正體漢字，以及香港獨有的文化，都應該繼續存在下去。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：kowaiyin.yoyoko<br />\n<br />\n逢星期一至六刊登<br />\n<br />\n===========<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0839a6912b510de648479b2a4b4ebceec12540a9","tid":2305888,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:44:59.000Z","msg":"放棄把啦，台灣後生嗰啲都少咗講台語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfc8bb440b7c9921d4d42201e9077b238913570","tid":2305888,"uid":114072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0839a6912b510de648479b2a4b4ebceec12540a9","tid":2305888,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:44:59.000Z","msg":"放棄把啦，台灣後生嗰啲都少咗講台語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:46:00.000Z","msg":"放你老味"}]}